This is a kind of cooperative bank

77
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:44,319
when members pull their savings together

78
00:04:44,319 --> 00:04:46,479
so they can lend funds to each other.

79
00:04:46,479 --> 00:04:48,079
Each member chips in,

80
00:04:48,079 --> 00:04:50,120
everyone gives a small amount of money

81
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:51,560
to pay for something together.

82
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:53,399
Getting back to vegetables,

83
00:04:53,399 --> 00:04:56,959
I think it's time to reveal the answer to my question, Beth.

84
